TITLE: Type-safe workers - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use TypeScript to define the type of a spawned worker function, improving type safety. It defines a `HashFunction` type and uses it when spawning the worker. The `spawn` function is parameterized with the type of the worker's exposed function.
