TITLE: Terminating a Thread Pool in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to terminate a thread pool using the `terminate()` method. You can either terminate gracefully, waiting for all tasks to complete, or force-terminate immediately.
SOURCE: https://github.com/andywer/threads.js/blob/master/docs/usage-pool.md#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
// Terminate gracefully
pool.terminate()

// Force-terminate pool workers
pool.terminate(true)
```

